Title: HiTIMED
Description: The HiTIMED package contains reference libraries derived from Illumina HumanMethylation450K and DNA methylation microarrays (Zhang Z, Salas LA et al. 2022) from public resources.
Notes: Zhang Z et al 2022, Farkas SA et al 2013, Zhang W et al 2020, Timp W et al 2014, Lennard K et al 2016
